Goldman Sachs $2 Billion Islamic Bond Prospectus Approved

-- B y   J o e   B r e n n a n
-- 
2011-10-19T15:59:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/goldman-sachs-2-billion-islamic-bond-prospectus-approved.html
Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS) ’s filing of
prospectus for a $2 billion Islamic bond program for listing on
the Irish Stock Exchange has been approved by the Central Bank
of Ireland.  New York-based bank’s Goldman Sachs International unit set
up Global Sukuk Company Limited, which is incorporated in the
 Cayman Islands , as trustee and seller of so-called murabaha
trust certificates, according to the prospectus, published on
the Dublin-based central bank’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joe Brennan in Dublin at 
 jbrennan29@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dara Doyle at 
 ddoyle1@bloomberg.net  